                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-75-18601126 t18601126-75-punishment-70"></join>Confined Eighteen Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The following case has been omitted from the Old Court, Thursday.</hi>
